translation[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,91,"Aur woh khaatun jisne apni ismat (chastity) ki hifazat ki thi, humne uske andar apni rooh se phoonka aur usey aur uske bete ko duniya bhar ke liye nishani bana diya"
  21,92,"Yeh tumhari ummat haqeeqat mein ek hi ummat hai aur main tumhara Rubb hoon, pas tum meri ibadat karo"
  21,93,"Magar (yeh logon ki karastani hai ke) inhon ne aapas mein deen ko tukde tukde kar dala, sabko hamari taraf palatna hai"
  21,94,"Phir jo neik amal karega, is haal mein ke woh momin ho, to uske kaam ki na-qadri na hogi, aur usey hum likh rahey hain"
  21,95,Aur mumkin nahin hai ke jis basti ko humne halaak kardiya ho woh phir palat sakey
  21,96,Yahaan tak ke jab yajooj majooj khol diye jayenge aur har bulandi se woh nikal padenge
  21,97,"Aur wada bar haqq ke poora hone ka waqt qareeb aa lagega to yakayak un logon ke deedhey phatey ke phatey reh jayenge (fixedly stare in horror), jinhon ne kufr kiya tha. Kahenge “haaye hamari kambakhti, hum is cheez ki taraf se gaflat mein padey huey thay, balke hum khatakaar thay.”"
  21,98,"Beshak tum aur tumhare woh mabood jinhein tum poojhte ho, jahannum ka indhan (fuel) hain, wahin tumko jana hai"
  21,99,"Agar yeh waqayi khuda hotey to wahan na jatey, ab sabko hamesha usi mein rehna hai.”"
  21,100,Wahaan woh phunkare maarenge (groan/roar) aur haal yeh hoga ke usmein kaan padi aawaaz na sunayi degi
  21,101,"Rahey woh log jinke liye hamari taraf se bhalayi ka pehle hi faisla ho chuka hoga, to woh yaqeenan ussey door rakkhey jayenge"